{"word":"εὐχερής","slug":"εὐχερής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n45488\" key=\"eu)xerh/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εὐχερ-ής</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ές</itype>, <sense id=\"n45488.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tolerant of</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">indifferent to evil, unpleasantness</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inaccuracy, not squeamish</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἡ ὗς -έστατον πρὸς πᾶσαν τροφὴν ζῴων ἐστίν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:595a:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">595a18</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδενὸς γὰρ πώποτε ἀπέβαλεν ὀσπρίου λέπος· οὕτως ἐκεῖνός ἐστιν εὐ. ἀνήρ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0402.tlg001:266:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Alex.\">Alex.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">266.8</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0421.tlg001:12:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aristopho\">Aristopho</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.5</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg006.perseus-grc1:519\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">519</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg006.perseus-grc1:875\" default=\"N